preference.name: MELineLinkedIconsProperty
preference.preference_description: Specifies whether the manufacturing applications display a symbol beside a linked structure line in a product (when linked as MEConsumed) or for a linked line in a work area (for all occurrence types). Valid Values: No value. - The linked symbols are not displayed. fnd0bl_assigned_as - The linked symbols are displayed in a reference pane (product or work area), indicating that a product component or work area object is linked (for example, consumed or used) in a process pane. Assigning a value to this preference slows the product/process structure loading.
